item.title: CVE-2022-4657|2024-08-03T01:48:39.494Z -- unknown -- restaurant%20menu
item.description: The Restaurant Menu WordPress plugin before 2.3.6 does not validate and escape some of its shortcode attributes before outputting them back in a page/post where the shortcode is embed, which could allow users with the contributor role and above to perform Stored Cross-Site Scripting attacks
